{"id":231097105,"title":"很孤單","content":"前陣子好像看到校園內開始提倡減塑\n但每次去到附近的餐廳還是看到好多學生一樣使用免洗餐具 即使店家明明就有提供內用餐具\n也沒看過學生買飲料會自備杯子什麼的\n\n看了真的很無奈\n雖然說有男友跟我一起都自備餐具（餐盒 筷子 湯匙 杯子 吸管）\n但看到這種情況難免還是覺得孤單⋯\nhttps://i.imgur.com/MSNhy2l.jpg\n\n\n\n\n\n有哪些文藻寶貝願意露露臉讓我知道我並不孤單的嗎😢\n\n-減塑生活已維持三年多的孤單情侶檔","excerpt":"前陣子好像看到校園內開始提倡減塑，但每次去到附近的餐廳還是看到好多學生一樣使用免洗餐具 即使店家明明就有提供內用餐具，也沒看過學生買飲料會自備杯子什麼的，看了真的很無奈，雖然說有男友跟我一起都自備餐具（餐盒 筷子 湯匙 杯子 吸管）","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-04-15T17:41:40.258Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-15T17:42:59.917Z","commentCount":32,"likeCount":75,"tags":[],"topics":["心得","環保","無痕飲食","減塑","無痕"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"文藻外語大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":75}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/MSNhy2l.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"37ce4326-1b3a-469d-a1a8-433a7dd6154d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/MSNhy2l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/MSNhy2l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/MSNhy2l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-04-15T17:41:40.258Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-15T17:42:59.917Z"},{"id":"37ce4326-1b3a-469d-a1a8-433a7dd6154d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/MSNhy2l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/MSNhy2l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/MSNhy2l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-04-15T17:41:40.258Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-15T17:42:59.917Z"}],"postAvatar":""}